    </div>

    <p>The functional mushrooms in these products work through mechanisms entirely different from caffeine. Lion's mane stimulates nerve growth factor (NGF) — a protein critical for neuron growth and cognitive function. Cordyceps enhances cellular ATP production by supporting mitochondrial oxygen utilization. Chaga provides one of the highest antioxidant ORAC scores of any food. And reishi modulates the immune system while calming the nervous system through triterpene compounds. Together, these mushrooms provide sustained, jitter-free energy and focus that caffeine alone cannot match.</p>

